Detailed Description

This contains stub files for the MyUSB board drivers. If the MyUSB board drivers are used with board hardare other than those directly supported by the library, the BOARD parameter of the application's makefile can be set to "USER", and these stub files copied to the "/Board/" directory of the application's folder. When fleshed out with working driver code for the custom board, the corresponding MyUSB board APIs will work correctly with the non-standard board hardware.
